attributes.Long form description: The student assembles the stool, intertwines the legs, screws them, inserts the legs into the seat, mounts the saddle washers into the legs, screws the fours screws of the seat, tightens the screws, and finally tightens the middle hex nut.

attributes.Transcription: Hello and welcome to our study in front of you , you will see the parts needed to assemble a stool from IKEA.
Your task, for now, will be to please assemble the stool.

attributes.Action Correctness: Wrong Action, corrected by instructor verbally
attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: Leave the stool upright as you tighten it up.

attributes.Transcription: Please leave the feet upright as you tighten it up.

attributes.Action Correctness: Wrong Action, corrected by instructor verbally
attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student should make sure that the flat part of the nut is facing the feet.

attributes.Transcription: Please make sure that the flat part of the nut is facing the feet.

attributes.Action Correctness: Wrong Action, corrected by instructor verbally
attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student should leave the feet upright when you tighten the nut.

attributes.Transcription: Please leave the feet upright when you tighten the nut.

attributes.Action sentence: The student mounts the saddle washers and screws of the legs.

attributes.Transcription: Please flip the stool and tighten the center screw.

attributes.Action sentence: The student tightens the hex nut.

attributes.Transcription: That will be everything for the task.
you may now press the stop button.
